# Codex Instructions

## Codex Home

- Keep `CODEX_HOME` at the Codex default unless the user explicitly requests
  moving the whole Codex state directory.
- Do not treat `CODEX_HOME` as a config-only location. It contains Codex
  config, auth, logs, sessions, skills, plugins, cache, and other runtime
  state.
